      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Blind-bake the case",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Roll the {{shortcrust-pastry}} to 3 mm and line the 23 cm tart tin. Chill for 30 minutes. Preheat the oven to 190°C fan. Line with baking paper and beans. Blind-bake for 15 minutes. Remove the paper and beans, brush the base with beaten {{eggs}}, and bake for a further 5 minutes. Cool completely.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Make the crème pâtissière",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "See the ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "crème pâtissière",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmp99c1740001ycv42dgpsydi"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " note. Whisk the {{egg-yolks}}, {{caster-sugar}}, and {{cornflour}} in a bowl. Heat the {{whole-milk}} to just below a simmer and pour slowly over the egg mixture, whisking constantly. Return to the saucepan and cook over medium heat, stirring, until thick and bubbling. Cook for 2 more minutes. Off the heat, stir in the {{vanilla-extract}} and {{unsalted-butter}}. Press cling film onto the surface and cool to room temperature, then refrigerate.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Assemble and glaze",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Spread the cold crème pâtissière into the case in an even layer. Arrange the {{strawberries}}, {{raspberries}}, and {{blueberries}} tightly over the top. Warm the {{apricot-jam}} with a tablespoon of water and push through a sieve. Brush lightly over the fruit. Serve within 2 hours of assembling.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
